name: Abandonment of Regret
description: Let go of the past that still haunts you. Overcome the feelings of regret for past mistakes so that you may thrive after learning from them. You deserve to be happy, regardless of the gravity of your mistakes, as long as you put in the work to make things right. In collaboration with the wondrous Ras Al Hague's photography and modeling, and my photo editing and visual looping work.
